# Implementation style

- Do not create shared helpers, utilities, or cross-file abstractions unless explicitly requested.
- Wire behavior inline at the call site instead of extracting helpers.
- Do not add Python scripts or generate-* tooling unless explicitly requested.
- Do not introduce new shared modules for one-off tasks.
- Prefer the smallest direct diff that solves the request.
